            <div class="newsListBox newsListBox--top last-child linkedarea" data-href="/news-and-events/d-phys-news/2024/04/superfluid-surprise.html">
                <div class="info">
                    <h2>
                        
                            <a href="/news-and-events/d-phys-news/2024/04/superfluid-surprise.html">Superfluid surprise</a>
                        
                        
                    </h2>
                    
                        <div class="TagCloud TagCloud--raw TagCloud--newslist">
                            <ul class="TagCloud__list"><li class="TagCloud__item"><a class="eth-link" href="/news-and-events/d-phys-news.html?TAG=bmV3czpmb3JtYXRlL3BoeXNpaw&amp;path=L2NvbnRlbnQvc3BlY2lhbGludGVyZXN0L3BoeXMvZC1waHlzL2VuL2pjcjpjb250ZW50L3Bhci90d29jb2x1bW5fMC9wYXJfcmlnaHQvdGVhc2VyYm94XzkzNzk1MTA3Mi9wYXIvbmV3c2ZlZWQ">Physics</a></li><li class="TagCloud__item"><a class="eth-link" href="/news-and-events/d-phys-news.html?TAG=bmV3czpmb3JtYXRlL3BoeXNpay9xdWFudGVud2lzc2Vuc2NoYWZ0ZW4&amp;path=L2NvbnRlbnQvc3BlY2lhbGludGVyZXN0L3BoeXMvZC1waHlzL2VuL2pjcjpjb250ZW50L3Bhci90d29jb2x1bW5fMC9wYXJfcmlnaHQvdGVhc2VyYm94XzkzNzk1MTA3Mi9wYXIvbmV3c2ZlZWQ">Quantum sciences</a></li><li class="TagCloud__item"><a class="eth-link" href="/news-and-events/d-phys-news.html?TAG=c3BlY2lhbGludGVyZXN0OnBoeXMvcXVhbnR1bQ&amp;path=L2NvbnRlbnQvc3BlY2lhbGludGVyZXN0L3BoeXMvZC1waHlzL2VuL2pjcjpjb250ZW50L3Bhci90d29jb2x1bW5fMC9wYXJfcmlnaHQvdGVhc2VyYm94XzkzNzk1MTA3Mi9wYXIvbmV3c2ZlZWQ">Institute for Quantum Electronics (IQE)</a></li><li class="TagCloud__item"><a class="eth-link" href="/news-and-events/d-phys-news.html?TAG=c3BlY2lhbGludGVyZXN0OnBoeXM&amp;path=L2NvbnRlbnQvc3BlY2lhbGludGVyZXN0L3BoeXMvZC1waHlzL2VuL2pjcjpjb250ZW50L3Bhci90d29jb2x1bW5fMC9wYXJfcmlnaHQvdGVhc2VyYm94XzkzNzk1MTA3Mi9wYXIvbmV3c2ZlZWQ">D-PHYS</a></li></ul>
                        </div>
                    
                    <div class="text-image topstory">
                        
                            
                                <picture class="ResponsiveImage newsListBox__image">
                                    <img alt="Transport between two connected superfluid reservoirs" title="" src="/news-and-events/d-phys-news/2024/04/superfluid-surprise/_jcr_content/pageimages/imageBig.imageformat.topstory_fullwidth.546472529.jpg"/>
    
                                </picture>
                            
                        
                        
                            <p>Researchers from the Institute for Quantum Electronics and the Quantum Center studied particle and entropy flows between two connected superfluid reservoirs and found unexpected evidence of irreversible and enhanced entropy transport.</p>
                        
                        <div class="dateInfo">
                            <span class="dateInfo">
                                <time datetime="2024-04-25T00:00:00Z">25.04.2024</time>
                                
                            </span>
                            
                            
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        
            
            
            <div class="newsListBox newsListBox--top last-child linkedarea" data-href="https://ethz.ch/en/news-and-events/eth-news/news/2024/04/surprising-reversal-in-quantum-systems.html">
                <div class="info">
                    <h2>
                        
                            <a href="https://ethz.ch/en/news-and-events/eth-news/news/2024/04/surprising-reversal-in-quantum-systems.html">Surprising reversal in quantum systems</a>
                        
                        
                    </h2>
                    
                        <div class="TagCloud TagCloud--raw TagCloud--newslist">
                            <ul class="TagCloud__list"><li class="TagCloud__item"><a class="eth-link" href="https://ethz.ch/en/news-and-events/eth-news/news.html?TAG=bmV3czpmb3JtYXRlL3BoeXNpay9xdWFudGVud2lzc2Vuc2NoYWZ0ZW4&amp;path=L2NvbnRlbnQvc3BlY2lhbGludGVyZXN0L3BoeXMvZC1waHlzL2VuL2pjcjpjb250ZW50L3Bhci90d29jb2x1bW5fMC9wYXJfcmlnaHQvdGVhc2VyYm94XzkzNzk1MTA3Mi9wYXIvbmV3c2ZlZWQ">Quantum sciences</a></li><li class="TagCloud__item"><a class="eth-link" href="https://ethz.ch/en/news-and-events/eth-news/news.html?TAG=bmV3czpmb3JtYXRlL3BoeXNpay9waHlzaWs&amp;path=L2NvbnRlbnQvc3BlY2lhbGludGVyZXN0L3BoeXMvZC1waHlzL2VuL2pjcjpjb250ZW50L3Bhci90d29jb2x1bW5fMC9wYXJfcmlnaHQvdGVhc2VyYm94XzkzNzk1MTA3Mi9wYXIvbmV3c2ZlZWQ">Physics</a></li></ul>
                        </div>
                    
                    <div class="text-image topstory">
                        
                            
                                <picture class="ResponsiveImage newsListBox__image">
                                    <img alt="" title="" src="https://ethz.ch/en/news-and-events/eth-news/news/2024/04/surprising-reversal-in-quantum-systems/_jcr_content/pageimages/imageBig.imageformat.topstory_fullwidth.250296132.jpg"/>
    
                                </picture>
                            
                        
                        
                            <p>Researchers at ETH Zurich have studied topological effects in an artificial solid, making surprising observations. The new insights into topological pumping could be used for quantum technologies in the future.</p>
                        
                        <div class="dateInfo">
                            <span class="dateInfo">
                                <time datetime="2024-04-18T00:00:00Z">18.04.2024</time>
                                
                            </span>
                            
                            
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        
            
            
