                <div class="info">
                    <h2>
                        
                            <a href="/news-and-events/d-phys-news/2024/04/berezinskii-kosterlitz-thouless-phase-transition-on-the-lattice-without-fine-tuning-by-qubit-regularisation.html">A qubit regularisation of asymptotic freedom without fine tuning</a>
                        
                        
                    </h2>
                    
                        <div class="TagCloud TagCloud--raw TagCloud--newslist">
                            <ul class="TagCloud__list"><li class="TagCloud__item"><a class="eth-link" href="/news-and-events/d-phys-news.html?TAG=bmV3czpmb3JtYXRlL3BoeXNpaw&amp;path=L2NvbnRlbnQvc3BlY2lhbGludGVyZXN0L3BoeXMvZC1waHlzL2VuL2pjcjpjb250ZW50L3Bhci90d29jb2x1bW5fMC9wYXJfcmlnaHQvdGVhc2VyYm94XzkzNzk1MTA3Mi9wYXIvbmV3c2ZlZWQ">Physics</a></li><li class="TagCloud__item"><a class="eth-link" href="/news-and-events/d-phys-news.html?TAG=c3BlY2lhbGludGVyZXN0OnBoeXMvdGhlb3JldGljYWw&amp;path=L2NvbnRlbnQvc3BlY2lhbGludGVyZXN0L3BoeXMvZC1waHlzL2VuL2pjcjpjb250ZW50L3Bhci90d29jb2x1bW5fMC9wYXJfcmlnaHQvdGVhc2VyYm94XzkzNzk1MTA3Mi9wYXIvbmV3c2ZlZWQ">Institute for Theoretical Physics (ITP)</a></li><li class="TagCloud__item"><a class="eth-link" href="/news-and-events/d-phys-news.html?TAG=c3BlY2lhbGludGVyZXN0OnBoeXM&amp;path=L2NvbnRlbnQvc3BlY2lhbGludGVyZXN0L3BoeXMvZC1waHlzL2VuL2pjcjpjb250ZW50L3Bhci90d29jb2x1bW5fMC9wYXJfcmlnaHQvdGVhc2VyYm94XzkzNzk1MTA3Mi9wYXIvbmV3c2ZlZWQ">D-PHYS</a></li><li class="TagCloud__item"><a class="eth-link" href="/news-and-events/d-phys-news.html?TAG=c3BlY2lhbGludGVyZXN0OnBoeXMvdGhlb3JldGljYWwvc2ltdWxhdGlvbmFsLXBoeXNpY3M&amp;path=L2NvbnRlbnQvc3BlY2lhbGludGVyZXN0L3BoeXMvZC1waHlzL2VuL2pjcjpjb250ZW50L3Bhci90d29jb2x1bW5fMC9wYXJfcmlnaHQvdGVhc2VyYm94XzkzNzk1MTA3Mi9wYXIvbmV3c2ZlZWQ">Simulational Physics</a></li></ul>
                        </div>
                    
                    <div class="text-image topstory">
                        
                            
                                <picture class="ResponsiveImage newsListBox__image">
                                    <img alt="" title="" src="/news-and-events/d-phys-news/2024/04/berezinskii-kosterlitz-thouless-phase-transition-on-the-lattice-without-fine-tuning-by-qubit-regularisation/_jcr_content/pageimages/imageBig.imageformat.topstory_fullwidth.7888154.png"/>
    
                                </picture>
                            
                        
                        
                            <p>Marina Marinkovic works to understand more about the strong force that binds quarks and gluons into hadrons as described by quantum chromodynamics.</p>
                        
                        <div class="dateInfo">
                            <span class="dateInfo">
