	    <div class="contentSubContainer noBorder contains-linklist contains-line">
		   
        
          
            <h2>Honours &amp; Awards</h2>
          
          
        
		   
           <div class="contextinfo parsys basecomponent section contains-linklist contains-line">

<a id="contextinfo_1955448866_newsfeed" style="visibility:hidden"></a>
        <div class="newsfeed basecomponent">
			
		
            
    <section class="block contentbox">
        <div class="newsList">
            
                
                
                <div data-href="/news-and-events/d-phys-news/2023/11/golden-owl-to-klaus-ensslin.html" class="newsListBox linkedarea">
                    <div class="info">
                        <h3>
                            
                                <a href="/news-and-events/d-phys-news/2023/11/golden-owl-to-klaus-ensslin.html">Golden Owl to Klaus Ensslin</a>
                             
                             
                        </h3>
                        
                        <div class="contentInfo">
	                        
	                        
	                        	<p>Klaus Ensslin received a Golden Owl award for his teaching activities in the Department of Physics. Every year, the ETH Zurich Student Association (VSETH) honours lecturers whose excellent teaching stands out with this award.</p>
	                        
	                        <div class="dateInfo">
	                            <span class="dateInfo">
	                                <time datetime="2023-11-20T00:00:00Z">20.11.2023</time>
	                                
	                            </span>
	                            
	                        </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            
                
                
                <div data-href="/news-and-events/d-phys-news/2023/09/snsf-funded-projects-start-for-elsa-abreu-and-puneet-anantha-murthy.html" class="newsListBox linkedarea">
                    <div class="info">
                        <h3>
                            
                                <a href="/news-and-events/d-phys-news/2023/09/snsf-funded-projects-start-for-elsa-abreu-and-puneet-anantha-murthy.html">SNSF-funded projects start for Elsa Abreu and Puneet Anantha Murthy</a>
                             
                             
                        </h3>
                        
                        <div class="contentInfo">
	                        
	                        
	                        	<p>The two researchers, who are members of the Institute for Quantum Electronics, were both awarded SNSF Starting Grants.</p>
	                        
	                        <div class="dateInfo">
	                            <span class="dateInfo">
	                                <time datetime="2023-09-29T00:00:00Z">29.09.2023</time>
	                                
	                            </span>
	                            
	                        </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            
                
                
                <div data-href="https://ethz.ch/en/the-eth-zurich/portrait/latest-honours-and-prizes/2023/04/didier-queloz-awarded-legiondhonneur.html" class="newsListBox last-child linkedarea">
                    <div class="info">
                        <h3>
                            
                                <a href="https://ethz.ch/en/the-eth-zurich/portrait/latest-honours-and-prizes/2023/04/didier-queloz-awarded-legiondhonneur.html">Didier Queloz awarded the Insigna of Knight of National Order of the “Légion d'honneur&quot;</a>
                             
                             
                        </h3>
                        
                        <div class="contentInfo">
	                        
	                        
	                        	<p>On 20 April 2023, Didier Queloz, Nobel Laureate in Physics 2019 and President of the Marcel Benoist Foundation, was awarded the Insignia of Knight of the National Order of the Legion of Honour by H.E.M. Frédéric Journès, the French Ambassador to Switzerland.</p>
	                        
	                        <div class="dateInfo">
	                            <span class="dateInfo">
	                                <time datetime="2023-04-25T00:00:00Z">25.04.2023</time>
	                                
	                            </span>
	                            
	                        </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            
        </div>
        
    </section>

		
		
	
	
</div>
<a id="contextinfo_1955448866_line" style="visibility:hidden"></a>
        <div class="line basecomponent"><div class="teaserboxline ">
    <div class="separator">
        <hr>
    </div>
</div></div>
